headline: Henry Schein One Launches Forms to Make Patient Check-In Easier and Faster
summary: AMERICAN FORK, Utah, July 30, 2025--Henry Schein One, the most connected solution in dental technology, today launched Forms for Dentrix and Dentrix Ascend (Ascend). With more than 1,000 dental practices adopting Forms just this month, this fully integrated digital intake solution is already simplifying the pre-appointment process for both patients and dental teams.
